ot therefore any more smite all living flesh as I have done. }22.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  All the days of the earth, seed and harvest, cold and heat, summer and spring, shall not cease by day or night. }1.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  And God blessed Noe and his sons, and said to them, Increase and multiply, a
nd fill the earth and have dominion over it. }2.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  And the dread and the fear of you shall be upon all the wild beasts of the earth, on all the birds of the sky, and on all things moving upon the earth, and upon all the fishes of the sea, I have placed them u
nder your power. }3.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  And every reptile which is living shall be to you for meat, I have given all things to you as the green herbs. }4.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  But flesh with blood of life ye shall not eat. }5.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  For your blood of your lives will I require at the hand of all wild beas
ts, and I will require the life of man at the hand of his brother man. }6.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  He that sheds man's blood instead of that blood shall his own be shed, for in the image of God I made man. }7.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  But do ye increase and multiply, and fill the earth, and have dominion o
ver it. }}
