s many as are with you, of all that come out of the ark. }11.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  And I will establish my covenant with you and all flesh shall not any more die by the water of the flood, and there shall no more be a flood of water to destroy all the earth }12.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  And the Lord God
 said to Noe, This is the sign of the covenant which I set between me and you, and between every living creature which is with you for perpetual generations. }13.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  I set my bow in the cloud, and it shall be for a sign of covenant between me and the earth. }14
.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  And it shall be when I gather clouds upon the earth, that my bow shall be seen in the cloud. }15.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  And I will remember my covenant, which is between me and you, and between every living soul in all flesh, and there shall no longer be water for a deluge, so
 as to blot out all flesh. }16.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  And my bow shall be in the cloud, and I will look to remember the everlasting covenant between me and the earth, and between every living soul in all flesh which is upon the earth. }17.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  And God said to Noe, This is the sign of
