pon us: we have made falsehood our hope, and by falsehood shall we be protected: }16.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  Therefore thus saith the Lord, [even] the Lord. Behold, I lay for the foundations of Sion a costly stone, a choice, a corner-stone, a precious [stone], for its foundations
; and he that believes [on him] shall by no means be ashamed. }17.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  And I will cause judgment [to be] for hope, and my compassion shall be for [just] measures, and ye that trust vainly in falsehood [shall fall]: for the storm shall by no means pass by you, }1
8.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  except it also take away your covenant of death, and your trust in Hades shall by no means stand: if the rushing storm should come upon you, ye shall be beaten down by it. }19.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  Whenever it shall pass by, it shall take you; morning by morning it shall pas
s by in the day, and in the night there shall be an evil hope. ??. Learn to hear, }20.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  ye that are distressed; we cannot fight, but we are ourselves too weak for you to be gathered. }21.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  Lord shall rise up as a mountain of ungodly [men], and shall be in the 
valley of Gabaon; he shall perform his works with wrath, [even] a work of bitterness, and his wrath shall deal strangely, and his destruction shall be strange. }22.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  Therefore do not ye rejoice, neither let your bands be made strong; for I have heard of work
