proceed to remove this people, and I will remove them: and I will destroy the wisdom of the wise, and will hide the understanding of the prudent. }15.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  Woe to them that deepen their counsel, and not by the Lord. Woe to them that take secret counsel, and whos
e works darkness, and they say, Who has seen us? }16.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  Shall ye not be counted as clay of the potter? Shall the thing formed say to him that formed it, Thou didst not form me? or the work to the maker, Thou hast not made me wisely? }17.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  [Is it] not yet a litt
le while, and Libanus shall be changed as the mountains of Chermel, and Chermel shall be reckoned as a forest? }18.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  And in that day the deaf shall hear the words of the book, and they that are in darkness, and they that are in mist: the eyes of the blind sh
all see, }19.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  and the poor shall rejoice with joy because of the Lord, and they that had no hope among men shall be filled with joy. }20.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  The lawless man has come to nought, and the proud man has perished, and they that transgress mischievously have been utt
erly destroyed: }21.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  and they that cause men to sin by a word: and men shall make all that reprove in the gates an offense, because they have unjustly turned aside the righteous. }22.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  Therefore this saith the Lord concerning the house of Jacob, whom he set a
part from Abraam, Jacob shall not now be ashamed, neither shall he now change countenance. }23.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  But when their children shall have seen my works, they shall sanctify my name for my sake, and they shall fear the God of Israel. }}
