\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s9\qj\rtlch\af5\afs20\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af5\langfe1033\hich\f5\fs20\lang1033\loch\f5\fs20\lang1033{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f4\fs24\lang1033\i\b0{\*\cs27\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs24\lang1033\i\loch\f4\fs24\lang1033\i Reader:}}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f5\fs20\lang1033\i0\b0  15.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  The simple believes every word: but the prudent man betakes himself to after-thought. }16.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  A wise man fears, and departs from evil; but the fool trusts in himself, and joins himself with the transgressor. }17.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  A passionate man acts inconsideratel
y; but a sensible man bears up under many things. }18.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  Fools shall have mischief for their portion; but the prudent shall take fast hold of understanding. }19.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  Evil men shall fall before the good; and the ungodly shall attend at the gates of the righteous. }2
0.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  Friends will hate poor friends; but the friends of the rich are many. }21.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  He that dishonors the needy sins: but he that has pity on the poor is most blessed. }22.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  They that go astray devise evils: but the good devise mercy and truth. The framers of evil 
do not understand mercy and truth: but compassion and faithfulness are with the framers of good. }23.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  With every one who is careful there is abundance: but the pleasure-taking and indolent shall be in want. }24.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  A prudent man is the crown of the wise: but th
e occupation of fools is evil. }25.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  A faithful witness shall deliver a soul from evil: but a deceitful man kindles falsehoods. }26.{\*\cs23\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f4\fs32\lang1033\loch\f4\fs32\lang1033  In the fear of the Lord is strong confidence: and he leaves his children a support. }}
